_json.gridTitle: Suran Kofta Curry Recipe - Yam Kofta Curry
_json.description: This delicious Suran Kofta Curry Recipe, is a sattvic recipe as the kofta curry is made without the use of onion and garlic and cooked in a delicious and mildly spiced tomato curry. The koftas are cooked in a paniyaram pan using less oil, yet they are made crisp on the outside and soft inside.Â  Suran/Elephant foot /yam is a versatile vegetable that can be cooked in various ways.
